30:10.820 --> 30:14.486
It just annoys me that somebody challenges all these things and you have to kind of solve it.

30:14.506 --> 30:15.568
But if you solve it and write it.

30:15.588 --> 30:16.730
They don't know.

30:16.770 --> 30:17.651
No, that's part of it, though.

30:17.671 --> 30:18.653
